reviews.text:
When you are queuing at the cashier, the staff shout out, "Please expect at least 30 minutes of waiting time."
What!? You choose McDonald's because it's fast food and you now need to wait longer?
This time I come here to try out their new 18-piece McNuggets combo and Shake-Shake Fries so I have no choice but to wait.
I found it more ridiculous when they got dozens of beverages and piles of burgers and racks of fries prepared and ready-to-serve. More staff at the back are making more burgers, fries and drinks, while there's only ONE cashier and ONE staff putting combos together to serve. And the staff is working so slow like you-deserve-slower-service.
Although I got my food in around 15 minutes, it's still trash to wait for so long and the people there has no sense of skilful workforce.
Nice place to go, but no McCafe.
Fair price! Good place for American food lover.
fast food everywere good service fast and cheap.
All McDonald in malls are nearby the playground for childs , so they would prefer to eat food here very much with its toys
